Class ParcelList

  • java.lang.Object
    • f21as.ParcelList

  • public class ParcelList
extends java.lang.Object
    ParcelList is a public class that handles a list of parcels in the depot. It uses a hashmap with specialized operations that can be used on it to add and retrieve parcels.
    Since:
    February, 2013
    Version:
    65
    Author:
    Amjad Bari, Wayne Muller, Sanaa Diab
